{
  "_README": "SOURCE OF TRUTH for fleet tooling — ONE correct way per concern. The guard (`just fleet-check`, CI .github/workflows/fleet-guard.yml) scans scripts/ for fleet tooling (launch_*, onstart_*, *_chunk_worker, fleet*, *_watch, *cost_watch) and FAILS if a script appears that is neither `canonical` nor `deprecated` here. Add a SUBCOMMAND to `scripts/jobsys/fleet`, not a new script. The `deprecated` forks are grandfathered (warn, not fail) until Phase E deletes them; --strict fails on them too.",
